  "contentHtml": "<figure><a href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!G5oc!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd54ee5e-407e-4691-9516-5111be456d11_1140x236.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/%24s_!G5oc!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd54ee5e-407e-4691-9516-5111be456d11_1140x236.png\" width=\"1140\" height=\"236\" data-size=\"normal\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n</a></figure>\n<p><em>The following page contains a list of NHL teams with their <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/how-my-nhl-elo-ratings-and-forecast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Elo ratings</a> and projected wins for the 2025-26 season. It also features Goals Above Replacement data, which is described <a href=\"https://github.com/Neil-Paine-1/NHL-Player-And-Team-Ratings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. Find the raw GAR and Elo data <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/historical-nhl-data-spreadsheet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">in the spreadsheet folder here</a>. Also, check out <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/t/updating-model\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">the other updating models here</a>.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/2025-26-nhl-elo-ratings-and-win-projections\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2025-26 NHL team Elo ratings and projections</a></strong></p></li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/upcoming-games\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Today’s game predictions</a></strong></p></li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/nhl-goals-above-replacement-leaderboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2025-26 NHL Goals Above Replacement leaderboard</a></strong></p></li>\n<li>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/historical-nhl-data-spreadsheet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Historical NHL data spreadsheet</a></strong></p>\n<hr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/2025-26-nhl-elo-ratings-and-win-projections\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2025-26 NHL team Elo ratings and projections</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/upcoming-games\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Today’s game predictions</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/nhl-goals-above-replacement-leaderboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2025-26 NHL Goals Above Replacement leaderboard</a></strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/i/175130233/historical-nhl-data-spreadsheet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Historical NHL data spreadsheet</a></strong></p>\n<hr>\n<h4>🏒 2025-26 NHL Elo ratings and win projections📉</h4>\n<p><em><strong>Note: </strong>These ratings start the 2025-26 season as a regressed version of <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2023-nhl-elo-ratings-and-win-projections\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">last year’s final ratings</a>.</em></p>\n<h4>🏒 Upcoming Games 👀</h4>\n<h4>❄️ 2025-26 NHL Goals Above Replacement leaderboard 🏒</h4>\n<h4>📊 Historical NHL Data Spreadsheet</h4>\n<p>Similar to in the NBA, this season paid subscribers will have access to a constantly updating spreadsheet of <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2023-nhl-elo-ratings-and-win-projections?open=false#%C2%A7nhl-goals-above-replacement-leaderboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Goals Above Replacement</a> and a variety of other advanced player metrics, plus historical team metrics and seasonal team Elo rating summaries for all of NHL history.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/subscribe?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>\n<p>The link for this year’s sheet is below the paywall:</p>\n<p>\n          <a href=\"https://neilpaine.substack.com/p/2025-26-nhl-team-elo-power-rankings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n              Read more\n          </a>\n      </p>",
